Stage 4 loadshedding will continue from 16:00 on Friday until 05:00 on Saturday morning. It will be downgraded to Stage 3 from 05:00 on Saturday until 05:00 on Sunday, after which it will again be reduced to Stage 2 until 16:00 on Sunday. Stage 3 will be implemented from 16:00 on Sunday until 05:00 on Monday. Over the last 24 hours, two generating units at Arnot, a unit each at Duvha, Kriel and Medupi, were taken offline for repairs, Eskom said.